To set up Apple Pay:
1. Go to Stripe Dashboard > Settings > Payment Methods > Apple Pay
2. Click "Add domain" and enter your domain (e.g. kiaanverse.com)
3. Download the verification file Stripe provides
4. Replace this entire file content with the downloaded file content
5. Deploy your site
6. Click "Verify" in the Stripe Dashboard

The file must be served at:
https://yourdomain.com/.well-known/apple-developer-merchantid-domain-association
